      <span class="section-kicker">Story</span>
      <h2>A garage that aims to keep things straightforward.</h2>
      <p>The business promise is simple: skilled mechanical work, sensible advice, and customer service that does not make people feel out of their depth. Whether the job is a sensor replacement, fault finding, routine servicing, or more involved repair work, the focus is on doing it properly and explaining things clearly.</p>
      <p>That matters because a lot of people still find garages intimidating. Nandrews is better positioned when the service feels professional, reliable, and approachable for every kind of driver.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="surface-card copy-card">
      <span class="section-kicker">Values</span>
      <h2>What customers should expect.</h2>
      <ul class="list-clean">
        <li>Friendly service without jargon or pressure.</li>
        <li>Honest diagnosis and clear next-step advice.</li>
        <li>Reasonable pricing and no hidden surprises where possible.</li>
        <li>Reliable workmanship from experienced mechanics.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

